     <h2>Our Commitment To You</h2> 
     <iframe width="330" height="195" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/v6yvW66-ThI?autohide=1&amp;rel0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe> 
     <p>Welcome to USC Verdugo Hills Hospital, now part of Keck Medicine of USC. USC Verdugo Hills is a 158-bed acute care hospital serving patients in the cities of Glendale and La Cañada Flintridge, as well as the surrounding Foothill communities of the San Gabriel Valley.</p> 
